title: #92Noon! Vikings talkers/Siny/RJ/ReggieWayne
description: A bunch of Vikings love on a Monday, assisted by Ron Johnson during the final hour, along with a fantastic Super Bowl Stories segment with former Colts WR Reggie Wayne! Calls throughout, and Dave Sinykin keeps hope alive for his 6-6 Packers.
